    "description": "《横冲直撞》（Crashy Laps）是一款享受驾驶和疯狂超车乐趣的游戏，最多可有4名玩家。短小却有趣的赛道正等着你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/5ee50b486488ec5bcdca5c0573847b22.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/5ee50b486488ec5bcdca5c0573847b22.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/5ee50b486488ec5bcdca5c0573847b22.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>而且，你可以在单机模式下，挑战每条赛道的最短时间成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/0f17fee4e1255c037226c24e49ecdbd7.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/0f17fee4e1255c037226c24e49ecdbd7.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/0f17fee4e1255c037226c24e49ecdbd7.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>-4种天时设定：早晨、中午、傍晚和夜晚。<br></li><li>-3种比赛模式：计时赛、大奖赛和锦标赛。<br></li><li>-4种可设置的地图：抓地力、环境……<br></li><li>-4条赛道在每张地图中：总计16条赛道。<br></li><li>-3种AI难度：新手、专业或行家。<br></li><li>-2种视角：等距或者俯视。<br></li><li>-2种引擎声：内燃机或电动发动机。<br></li><li>-个人定制：自定义赛车颜色和号码/名称。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/2dabf4d10bb6234afd84701ca99a91ac.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=600 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/2dabf4d10bb6234afd84701ca99a91ac.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/d0fee46991af10682a960e1ef35baed2.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=150 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/d0fee46991af10682a960e1ef35baed2.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/d0fee46991af10682a960e1ef35baed2.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/68b8e376d04074dfaecac51ce8ed22b8.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=150 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/68b8e376d04074dfaecac51ce8ed22b8.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/68b8e376d04074dfaecac51ce8ed22b8.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/61b60b58c8c85d57d99866ad9427e487.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=150 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/61b60b58c8c85d57d99866ad9427e487.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/61b60b58c8c85d57d99866ad9427e487.mp4?